Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
enc_source_continue_on_error(25.10)        enc_source_continue_on_error(25.10)

Name
       enc_source_continue_on_error

Syntax
        enc_source_continue_on_error <value>

       Type: Boolean

       Default: false

       Enables or disables source command to continue the script on tcl error.
       When  set  to  true, the source command will ignore tcl errors and con-
       tinue processing the script files. When set to false, a tcl error  will
       halt the script.

Example
       In  the following example, the Tcl File (test.tcl) has an error i.e. no
       option specified after hyphen (-) for the setDesignMode command in  the
       script.

       test.tcl content:

       ::::::::::::

       puts "Testing Script for Errors"

       setDesignMode -

       puts "End Testing Script for errors"

       ::::::::::::

       If  enc_source_continue_on_error  is set to false, and setDesignMode is
       specified with hyphen only (without the option name after the  hyphen),
       the  script will end and will not source other commands mentioned after
       setDesignMode.

       innovus 3> set enc_source_continue_on_error false

       false

       innovus 4> source test.tcl

       Testing Script for Errors

       Usage: setDesignMode [-help]  [-reset]  [-addPhysicalCell  {hier|flat}]
       [-congEffort        {low|medium|high|auto}]       [-dual_rail_via_pitch
       <min_via_pitch> <min_filler_via_pitch> <cell_boundary_spacing>]  [-ear-
       lyClockFlow  {true|false}]  [-expressRoute  {true|false}]  [-flowEffort
       {express|standard|extreme}]    [-ignore_followpin_vias    {true|false}]
       [-pessimisticMode    {true|false}]    [-powerEffort    {none|low|high}]
       [-process <integer>] [-slackWeighting  {unityWeighting|viewBasedWeight-
       ing}]

       **ERROR:  (IMPTCM-48):   ""-"" is not a legal option for command ""set-
       DesignMode"". Either the current option or an option prior to it is not
       specified correctly.

       If enc_source_continue_on_error is set to true,  and  setDesignMode  is
       specified  with hyphen only (without the option name after the hyphen),
       the script will throw an error and continue to source  the  other  com-
       mands without exiting.

       innovus 5> set enc_source_continue_on_error true

       true

       innovus 6> source test.tcl

       Testing Script for Errors

       Usage:  setDesignMode  [-help]  [-reset] [-addPhysicalCell {hier|flat}]
       [-congEffort       {low|medium|high|auto}]        [-dual_rail_via_pitch
       <min_via_pitch>  <min_filler_via_pitch> <cell_boundary_spacing>] [-ear-
       lyClockFlow  {true|false}]  [-expressRoute  {true|false}]  [-flowEffort
       {express|standard|extreme}]    [-ignore_followpin_vias    {true|false}]
       [-pessimisticMode    {true|false}]    [-powerEffort    {none|low|high}]
       [-process  <integer>] [-slackWeighting {unityWeighting|viewBasedWeight-
       ing}]

       **ERROR: (IMPTCM-48):   ""-"" is not a legal option for command  ""set-
       DesignMode"". Either the current option or an option prior to it is not
       specified correctly.

       **ERROR: (IMPSE-110):   File 'test.tcl' line 2: errors out.

       End Testing Script for errors

